Text: RE Golf BallsPST I can get the Titleist Enron for per dozen I will pay per dozen for your pinnacle Prices are going to drop fast on these so time is very important wrote I figure you are going to turn around and sell them on Ebaycurrent price is So I will sell you the two pinnacle cases for roughly a sleeve I now have two cases of the titleist golf balls that will also sell at the same price I can send you a picture tonight when I get home I can ship tomorrow or Saturday I will pay for the shipping If you are interested let me know Thanks PL Original Message From Anna Brown ENRON Sent Thursday January PM To Love Phillip M Subject Re Golf Balls yes I am interested in your Golf Balls Please email your best price for all of them shipped priority mail insured Priority mail usually runs for a dozen plus for the st of insurance I can send payment via paypal for them If you have a picture showing the boxes that would be great also Love Phillip M PhillipM NRONcom wrote Greg Couch forwarded your email address to me saying you were interested in some Enron logo sleeves of golf balls I have four sleeves of Titleist Tour Prestige and sleeves of Pinnacle Gold Distance golf balls Please let me know if you are interested and what you are willing to pay I am going to put them on EBay tonight if I do not here from you If you are not interested I apologize for the message Thanks
